I"ﬁ<p>A template which I use for making big decisions: <a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/19lXmZuv8YIA1jej7UHDh1f-uyanNsTjFB_QaYZNq_Zw/edit?usp=sharing">Taking a decision on X</a></p>

